{"id":91,"title":"测试开发工程师（SDET）到底在做什么？","slug":"测试开发工程师（SDET）到底在做什么？-1766595067","excerpt":"","content":"### 测试开发工程师（SDET）到底在做什么？\n\n\n\n\n\n## 1. 职责范围\n\n\n\n\n\n## 2. 与传统角色的区别\n\n\n\n\n\n## 3. 典型工作流程（举例）\n\n1. **需求同步**\n\n1. **测试方案设计**\n\n1. **自动化实现**\n\n1. **CI/CD 集成**\n\n1. **监控与分析**\n\n1. **持续改进**\n\n\n\n## 4. 必备技能栈\n\n\n\n\n\n## 5. 常见产出物\n\n- **自动化测试仓库**：可重复执行的脚本 + DSL + 数据集\n\n- **质量平台**：一站式查看覆盖率、缺陷趋势、性能基线\n\n- **Mock/Stub 服务**：脱离后端也能跑完端到端用例\n\n- **性能/稳定性报告**：TPS、P95、内存泄漏、ANR、Crash 分析\n\n- **质量度量体系**：漏检率、逃逸率、MTTR、SLO/SLA 报告\n\n\n\n## 6. 职业发展路径\n\n\n\n\n\n### 一句话总结\n\n\u003e 测试开发就是用“开发者思维”做“质量保障”——写代码、搭框架、建指标，让 Bug 更难闯入生产环境，发布更快、更稳、更安全。\n\n","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"PUBLIC","status":"PUBLISHED","published_at":"2025-12-25T00:51:07.061387+08:00","last_edited_at":"2025-12-25T00:51:07.061387+08:00","notion_page_id":"1f45d23c-2eec-80d2-bd4e-e055cf77514e","notion_last_edit":"2025-05-19T02:53:00Z","author_id":1,"author":{"id":1,"username":"admin","email":"admin@example.com","role":"ADMIN","is_verified":true,"is_active":true,"avatar":"","bio":"","last_login_at":"2025-12-20T00:47:21.462367+08:00","email_verified_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:23.810219+08:00","created_at":"2025-12-19T09:00:38.872854652Z","updated_at":"2026-03-09T22:24:24.010602+08:00","is_admin":true},"stats":{"id":91,"blog_post_id":91,"blog_post":{"id":0,"title":"","slug":"","excerpt":"","content":"","tags":"","categories":"","cover_image_url":"","access_level":"","status":"","author_id":0,"author":{"id":0,"username":"","email":"","role":"","is_verified":false,"is_active":false,"avatar":"","bio":"","created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","is_admin":false},"created_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","updated_at":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z"},"view_count":0,"like_count":0,"share_count":0,"comment_count":0,"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.621588+08:00","updated_at":"2025-12-25T00:54:02.621588+08:00"},"created_at":"2025-12-25T00:51:07.061387+08:00","updated_